The command `pyspider` is running pyspider in `all` mode which means all components needed is running automatically and connect them with python built-in message queue.

But the command `pyspider webui --cdn https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/` only run the `webui` component. To specify a parameter for component as well as using `all` mode, you can use a `config.json`:

```
{
  "webui": {
    "cdn": "https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/"
  }
}
```

and running with command `pyspider -c config.json`

